{"kanda":6,"sarga":78,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"निकुम्भंनिहतंश्रुत्वाकुम्भं च विनिपातितम् ।रावणःपरमामर्षीप्रजज्वालानलोयथा","trans":"On hearing that Nikumbha and Kumbha had been killed, Ravana was very furious and burning in anger.","words":[{"d":"निकुम्भम्","m":"Nikumbha"},{"d":"निहतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"कुम्भं च","m":"Kumbha and"},{"d":"विनिपातितम्","m":"had been killed"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"परमामर्षी","m":"very furious"},{"d":"अनलोयथा","m":"like fire"},{"d":"प्रजज्वाल","m":"burning in anger"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"नैरृतःक्रोधशोकाभ्यांद्वाभ्यांतुपरिमूर्छितः ।खरपुत्रंविशालाक्षंमकराक्षमचोदयत्","trans":"The Rakshasa king was overtaken by both anger and sorrow, bewildered excessively sent for broadeyed Makara, the son of Khara.","words":[{"d":"नैरृतः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"क्रोधशोकाभ्याम्","m":"overtaken by anger and sorrow"},{"d":"द्वाभ्याम्","m":"both"},{"d":"विशालाक्षम्","m":"broadeyed"},{"d":"खरपुत्रम्","m":"Khara's son"},{"d":"मकराक्षम्","m":"Makara Rakshasa"},{"d":"अचोदयत्","m":"sent for"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"गच्छपुत्रऽमयाऽजाज्ञप्तोबलेनाभिसमवनितः ।राघवंलक्ष्मणंचैवजहितांश्चवनौकसः","trans":"\"Son! commanded by me, you go accompanied by arm and kill the Vanaras, Raghava and Lakshmana aslo,","words":[{"d":"पुत्र","m":"son"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"अभिसमवनितः","m":"accompanied by army"},{"d":"गच्छ","m":"going"},{"d":"वनौकसः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"तां","m":"them"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणंचैव","m":"and Lakshman also"},{"d":"जहि","m":"kill"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"रावणस्यवचश्श्रुत्वाशूरमानीखरात्मजः ।बाढमित्यब्रवीद्धृष्टोमकराक्षोनिशाचरम्","trans":"Rejoicing to hear the words of Ravana, proclaiming himself to be a hero, Maka raksha, the son of Khara said 'good'.","words":[{"d":"शूरमानी","m":"proclaiming as hero"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"हृष्टः","m":"rejoiced"},{"d":"निशाचरम्","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"बाढम् इति","m":"good"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"सोऽभिवाद्यदशग्रीवंकृत्वाचापिप्रदक्षिणम् ।निर्जगामगृहाच्छुभ्राद्रावणस्याज्ञयाबली","trans":"Greeting the tenheaded Rakshasa and going round him according to tradition, the mighty warrior went out from the abode early morning by the command of Ravana.","words":[{"d":"बली","m":"mighty"},{"d":"दशग्रीवम्","m":"tenheaded"},{"d":"अभिवाद्य","m":"greeting"},{"d":"प्रदक्षिणंकृत्वाचापि","m":"also going round him as tradition"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"आज्ञया","m":"by order"},{"d":"शुभ्रात्","m":"early morning"},{"d":"गृहात्","m":"from the abode"},{"d":"निर्जगाम","m":"went out."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"समीपस्थंबलाध्यक्षंखरपुत्रोऽब्रवीदिदम् ।रथश्चानीयतांशीघ्रंसैन्यंत्वानीयतांत्वरात्","trans":"Khara's son spoke to the commanderinchief of the army standing nearby 'Let the chariot be brought quickly and the army proceed'.","words":[{"d":"समीपस्थम्","m":"nearby"},{"d":"बलाधक्षम्","m":"commanderinchief of the army"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"आनीयताम्","m":"brought"},{"d":"सैन्यम्","m":"army"},{"d":"त्वरात्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"आनीयताम्","m":"proceed"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"तस्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वाबलाध्यक्षोनिशाचरः ।स्यन्दनं च बलंचैवसमीपंप्रत्यपादयत् ।6.78.7।।","trans":"Upon hearing those words, the commanderinchief of the Rakshasas responded and placed the army near him.","words":[{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"तत् वचनम्","m":"those words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"बलाध्यक्षः","m":"commanderinchief"},{"d":"निशाचरः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"स्यन्दनं च","m":"responded"},{"d":"बलंचैव","m":"army too"},{"d":"समीपम्","m":"near"},{"d":"प्रत्यपादयत्","m":"placed near"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"प्रदक्षिणंरथंकृत्वाआरुरोहनिशाचरः ।सूतंसञ्चोदयामासशीघ्रंमेरथमावह","trans":"After having gone round the chariot he (Makara) ascended and said to the charioteer, 'let the chariot be driven quickly'.","words":[{"d":"निशाचरः","m":"night ranger"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"प्रदक्षिणंकृत्वा","m":"after having gone round"},{"d":"सूतम्","m":"charioteer"},{"d":"आरुरोह","m":"ascended मेmy"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"आवह","m":"get"},{"d":"सञ्चोदयामास","m":"drive the chariot"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"अथतान्राक्षसान्सर्वान्मकराक्षोऽब्रवीदिदम् ।यूयंसर्वेप्रयुध्यध्वंपुरस्तान्ममराक्षसाः","trans":"Thereafter, Maka raksha spoke to all Rakshasas, 'All of you be ahead of me and fight violently'.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"तान्","m":"his"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"यूयम्","m":"all of you"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"पुरस्तात्","m":"ahead"},{"d":"प्रयुध्यध्वम्","m":"fight violently"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"अहंराक्षसराजेनरावणेनमहात्मना ।आज्ञप्तःसमरेहन्तुंतावुभौरामलक्ष्मणौ","trans":"\"I will kill both Rama and Lakshmana in the battle, by the order of Ravana, the king of Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"राक्षसराजेन","m":"by Rakshasa king's"},{"d":"महात्मना","m":"great self"},{"d":"रावणेन","m":"to Ravana"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"तौ","m":"those"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणौ","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"उभौ","m":"both"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"will kill"},{"d":"आज्ञप्तः","m":"by his order"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"अद्यरामंवधिष्यामिलक्ष्मणं च निशाचराः ।शाखामृगं च सुग्रीवंवानरांश्चशरोत्तमैः","trans":"\"Now I shall put an end to Rama and Lakshmana, Sugriva and the Vanaras with the best of arrows.\"","words":[{"d":"निशाचराः","m":"night ranger"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"now"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणं च","m":"and Lakshmana"},{"d":"शाखामृगम्","m":"Vanara"},{"d":"सुग्रीवं च","m":"Sugriva also"},{"d":"वानरान् च","m":"Vanaras also"},{"d":"शरोत्तमैः","m":"best of arrows"},{"d":"वधिष्यामि","m":"will put an end"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"अद्यशूलनिपातैश्चवानराणांमहाचमूम् ।प्रदहिष्यामिसम्प्राप्तांशुष्केन्धनमिवानलः","trans":"\"Going there now, I will terminate the great Vanara army with these pikes just as drywood is burnt by fire.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"now"},{"d":"सम्प्राप्ताम्","m":"going there"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"महाचमूम्","m":"great army"},{"d":"अनलः","m":"fire"},{"d":"शुष्केन्धनमिव","m":"burns dry wood"},{"d":"शूलनिपातैः","m":"with these pikes"},{"d":"प्रदहिष्यामि","m":"will burn"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"मकराक्षस्यतच्छ्रुत्वावचनंतेनिशाचराः ।सर्वेनानायुधोपेताबलवन्तःसमाहिताः","trans":"On hearing Maka raksha's words all the mighty Rakshasas came with different kinds of weapons.","words":[{"d":"तत्","m":"then"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"बलवन्तः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"निशाचराः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"तेकामरूपिणस्सरेदंष्ट्रिणःपिङ्गलेक्षणा ।मातङ्गाइवनर्दन्तोध्वस्तकेशाभयावहाः परिवार्यमहाकायामहाकायंखरात्मजम् ।अभिजघ्नुस्ततोहृष्टाश्चालयन्तोवसुन्धराम्","trans":"Those who could change their form at will, cruel, with protruding teeth, yellow eyes, dishevelled hair, of frightful appearance, huge like elephants surrounding the son of Khara went joyously forward shaking the earth.","words":[{"d":"कामरूपिणः","m":"who could change their form at will"},{"d":"क्रूराः","m":"cruel"},{"d":"दंष्ट्रिणः","m":"protruding teeth"},{"d":"पिङ्गलेक्षणाः","m":"yellow eyes"},{"d":"महाकायाः","m":"huge body size"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"मातङ्गाःइव","m":"like elephants"},{"d":"महाकायम्","m":"of huge size"},{"d":"खरात्मजम्","m":"son of Khara"},{"d":"परिवार्य","m":"surrounding"},{"d":"वसुन्धराम्","m":"earth"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"तेकामरूपिणस्सरेदंष्ट्रिणःपिङ्गलेक्षणा ।मातङ्गाइवनर्दन्तोध्वस्तकेशाभयावहाः परिवार्यमहाकायामहाकायंखरात्मजम् ।अभिजघ्नुस्ततोहृष्टाश्चालयन्तोवसुन्धराम्","trans":"Those who could change their form at will, cruel, with protruding teeth, yellow eyes, dishevelled hair, of frightful appearance, huge like elephants surrounding the son of Khara went joyously forward shaking the earth.","words":[{"d":"कामरूपिणः","m":"who could change their form at will"},{"d":"क्रूराः","m":"cruel"},{"d":"दंष्ट्रिणः","m":"protruding teeth"},{"d":"पिङ्गलेक्षणाः","m":"yellow eyes"},{"d":"महाकायाः","m":"huge body size"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"मातङ्गाःइव","m":"like elephants"},{"d":"महाकायम्","m":"of huge size"},{"d":"खरात्मजम्","m":"son of Khara"},{"d":"परिवार्य","m":"surrounding"},{"d":"वसुन्धराम्","m":"earth"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"शङ्खभेरीसहस्राणामाहतानांसमन्ततः ।क्ष्येळितास्फोटितानां च तत्रशब्दोमहानभूत्","trans":"There was a beating of drums, blowing of thousands of conchs, clapping of arms and great sound was heard.","words":[{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"आहतानाम्","m":"beating of drums"},{"d":"क्षेवळितास्फोटितानां च","m":"clappings of arms"},{"d":"महान्","m":"great"},{"d":"शब्धः","m":"sound"},{"d":"अभूत्","m":"heard"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"प्रभ्रष्टोऽथकरात्तस्यप्रतोदस्सारथेस्तदा ।पपातसहसादैवाद्ध्वजस्तस्यतुरक्षसः","trans":"There, the long whip dropped from the charioteer's hand and the Rakshasa's standard had fallen suddenly by divine will.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and there"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"करात्","m":"hand"},{"d":"तस्यरक्षसः","m":"that Rakshasa"},{"d":"ध्वजः","m":"standard"},{"d":"दैवात्","m":"by divine will"},{"d":"पपात","m":"fallen"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"तस्यतेरथसंयुक्ताहयाविक्रमवर्जिताः ।चरणैराकुलैर्गत्वादीनाःसास्रमुखाययुः","trans":"His horses yoked to the chariot went giving up their valour, faltering feet, desperate and shedding tears.","words":[{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"रथसंयुक्ताः","m":"yoke binding the chariot"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"चरणैः","m":"feet"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"going"},{"d":"सास्रमुखाः","m":"shedding tears"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"प्रवातिपवनस्तस्मिन् सपांसुःखरदारुणः ।निर्याणेतस्यरौद्रस्यमकराक्षस्यदुर्मतेः","trans":"At the departure of evil minded and angry Maka raksha, dreadful and violent wind blew carrying with crumbling dust.","words":[{"d":"रौद्रस्य","m":"angry"},{"d":"दुर्मतेः","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"तस्यमकराक्षस्य","m":"that Maka raksha"},{"d":"तस्मिन् निर्याणे","m":"at his departure"},{"d":"सपांसुः","m":"crumbling dust"},{"d":"खरदारुणः","m":"dreadful and violent"},{"d":"पवनः","m":"wind"},{"d":"प्रवाति","m":"blowed."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"तानिदृष्टवानिमित्तानिराक्षसावीर्यवत्तमाः ।अचिन्त्यनिर्गतास्सर्वेयत्रतौरामलक्ष्मणौ","trans":"Seeing those portents incidentally and not taking into account those Rakshasas went where Rama and Lakshmana were.","words":[{"d":"वीर्यवत्तमाः","m":"exceedingly valiant"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"तानि","m":"them"},{"d":"निमित्तानि","m":"incidentally"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"अचिन्त्य","m":"not taking into account"},{"d":"तौ","m":"those"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणौ","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"यत्र","m":"there"}]}]}